def is_dishwasher_open(dishwasher:item):
    # Function to check if the dishwasher is open
    symbol is_open=open(dishwasher)
    return is_open

behavior put_dish_soap(dish_soap:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        if is_dishwasher_open(dishwasher):
            # If the dishwasher is already open, put the dish soap inside
            achieve inside(dish_soap, dishwasher)
        else:
            # If the dishwasher is not open, open it before putting the dish soap inside
            achieve_once open(dishwasher)
            achieve inside(dish_soap, dishwasher)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher
        bind dish_soap: item where:
            is_soap(dish_soap)
        # Select dish soap
        put_dish_soap(dish_soap, dishwasher)

def is_dishwasher_located(dishwasher:item):
    # Determine whether a dishwasher has been located
    symbol located=visited(dishwasher)
    return located

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        if exists dishwasher: item : is_dishwasher(dishwasher) and is_dishwasher_located(dishwasher)
:
            # If we have already located a dishwasher, we can approach it
            bind dishwasher: item where:
                is_dishwasher(dishwasher) and is_dishwasher_located(dishwasher)
            achieve close_char(char, dishwasher)
        else:
            # Otherwise, check all unvisited dishwashers
            foreach dishwasher: item:
                if is_dishwasher(dishwasher) and not visited(dishwasher):
                    observe(dishwasher, "Checking if the item is a dishwasher")
